RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select network_code,network_desc,ccy_code,clearing_System_prop,clearing_System_code from Istms_network_code where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A' order by network_code
select customer_no from STTM_CORE_CUSTOMER where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A' order by CUSTOMER_NO
select bic_code,bank_name from ISTMS_BIC_DIRECTORY where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A'order by bic_code

select distinct country_code, description from (select a.country_code, a.description from sttms_country a, cytms_ccy_country_map_master b where a.record_stat = 'O' and a.auth_stat = 'A' and a.country_code = b.country_code) where 1 = 1 order by 1
SELECT CLEARING_CODE, CLEARING_CODE_DESC FROM ISTMS_CLEARING_CODE WHERE network_CODE = ? AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' order by clearing_code
